{"tid":1905741,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台長呼籲 : 若有功能組別選票，你係不應該投票！或你可以投 白票  ！","createTime":"2020-03-01T12:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:21:34.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"61f50802c806ee2bb68711548a35f4fa47818535","tid":1905741,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LlWYy9XxZTI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLlWYy9XxZTI&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGolKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0a028575\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LlWYy9XxZTI</a><br />\n<br />\n1:56<br />\n<br />\n台長：第一件事嘅嘢就係你有冇票先，唔係人人都有<br />\n以我為例，我從事新聞界多年都冇票。<br />\n<br />\n第二，如果你有票，咁你嘅取態應該係點樣樣呢<br />\n出面有個講法就係區議會咁成功，我哋可以在下一成<br />\n但我想問嘅問題就係：如果你繼續維持呢個不公平的制度底下，咁幾時先有得改變？！<br />\n所以你嘅問題好簡單，如果你功能組別有票，係唔應該去投票，或者投白票！"},{"pid":"add9d65b3e4ef7c71fb8d5f6caae3826b11f4cf3","tid":1905741,"uid":39167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e529bf9a77779ce41376447f52976bf6d9e57a7c","tid":1905741,"uid":27411,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉</span></span>"},{"pid":"fedc4d84997ec8b372774fb9a2f78e0bd3b219c9","tid":1905741,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"但我想問嘅問題就係：如果你繼續維持呢個不公平的制度底下，咁幾時先有得改變？！<br />\n所以你嘅問題好簡單，如果你功能組別有票，係唔應該去投票，或者投白票！<br />\n<br />\n一個好基本既邏輯問題<br />\n唔投，繼續俾保皇維持住個位<br />\n先precisely係維持現狀，冇改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f175bb010e73e6e1e53dba96ee9cef4a3eb513","tid":1905741,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"事先聲明：梁錦祥咁講我咁quote <br />\n唔好話我老屈"},